Target Column: ClosePrice
- The amount of money paid by the purchaser to the seller for the property under the agreement
- Note: Do not use ListPrice or OriginalListPrice as features in machine learning models, they introduce data leakage and can artificially inflate model performance.

Key Columns
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
General Information
- PropertyType                    Types of properties, only interested in Residential Properties
- PropertySubType                 Subtypes to given property types, only interested in SingleFamilyResidence
- LotSizeSquareFeet               Total square footage of the lot
- LotSizeAcres                    Total acerage of the lot
- BuildingAreaTotal               Total area of the structure
- BathroomsTotalInteger           Number of bathrooms
- LivingArea                      Total livable area within structure
- Flooring                        List of all types of flooring
- Stories                         Number of floors
- GarageSpaces                    Number of garage spaces
- CoveredSpaces                   Number of garage and carport spaces

Amenities
- ViewYN                          Whether the property has a view
- WaterfrontYN                    Whether the property is on the waterfront
- BasementYN                      Whether the property has a basement
- PoolPrivateYN                   Whether the property has a private pool
- FireplaceYN                     Whether the property has a fireplace
- FireplacesTotal                 Number of fireplaces
- AttatchedGarageYN               Whether the property has an attached garage

Location
- Latitude                        Geographical latitude of the property
- Longitude                       Geographical longitude of the property
- City                            City on listing address
- StateorProvince                 Postal abbreviation for state or province of the property
- Postal Code                     Postal code of the property 
- ElementarySchoolDistrict        Elementary school district the property falls under            
- MiddleOrJuniorSchoolDistrict    Middle or junior school district the property falls under             
- HighSchoolDistrict              High school district the property falls under 
- TaxAnnualAmount                 Annual property tax amount for the property

Dates
- YearBuilt                       Year an occupancy permit is first granted for the property
- CloseDate                       Date the purchase agreement was fulfilled for the property
- DaysOnMarket                    Number of days the listing is on market
